ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS, in order to allow Quebec to fully exert its authority under the Canada-Quebec Accord to select entrepreneur immigrants and the flexibility to make changes to its entrepreneur immigrant program in response to provincial economic priorities.
